# Run the Fast-Model A/B

## Question

Flip llm.model in the local config to the ranked candidate, run several days
of real calls on each arm, and decide on receipts: TTFT distribution (Convex
turn rows) + judge quality scores + Joel's felt verdict. HITL because Joel
makes the calls and the call. Resolved when a model decision is recorded with
before/after numbers — and the loop has thereby proven it can measure a
tuning.
